    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="section about" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
      <div class="container about__grid">
        <figure class="about__media">
          <img
            src="/assets/images/founder.webp"
            alt="Arnaldo Laurencio, founder of Flor de Pita, smoking a hand-rolled cigar"
            class="about__image about__image--founder"
            loading="lazy"
            width="1088"
            height="928"
          />
          <figcaption class="about__caption">Arnaldo Laurencio, founder of Flor de Pita, est. 1968</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <div class="about__content">
          <p class="eyebrow">The Birth of the Greatest Cigar</p>
          <h2 class="section-heading about__heading" id="about-heading">
            A Family Legacy Since 1968
          </h2>
          <div class="about__body">
            <p>
              The legend behind Flor de Pita is Arnaldo Laurencio, who established
              the company in 1968. Born and raised in Camag&uuml;ey, Cuba, one of
              the most storied cigar regions in the world, he was infatuated with
              cigars from the very beginning. From the day he opened his cigar store,
              he wanted nothing more than to provide his friends and family with the
              best cigars around.
            </p>
            <p>
              His goal was simple: obtain the finest tobacco there is. Today his
              grandson, Erik, continues that legacy: every Pita cigar is still
              hand-rolled in small batches, using Nicaraguan long-filler tobacco and
              the same techniques passed down through three generations. Nothing
              shortcut, nothing outsourced.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="gold-rule" role="presentation"></div>
          <div class="about__stats" role="list">
            <div class="about__stat" role="listitem">
              <span class="about__stat-number">58</span>
              <span class="about__stat-label">Years of Craft</span>
            </div>
            <div class="about__stat" role="listitem">
              <span class="about__stat-number">3</span>
              <span class="about__stat-label">Generations</span>
            </div>
            <div class="about__stat" role="listitem">
              <span class="about__stat-number">100%</span>
              <span class="about__stat-label">Hand-Rolled</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

